t whether Vexa hears two named speakers in Google Meet.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:06:06.518599","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:02:27.271000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:02:37.483000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-2:0"},{"start":47.199,"end":59.912,"text":"First checkpoint, a developer calls the API Gateway, asks for a bot to join, and Vexa handles browser control audio capture and cleanup.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:06:36.540105","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:02:47.290000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:00.003000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-1:2"},{"start":64.653,"end":75.389,"text":"I hear you. The second checkpoint is speaker labels. The listener transcript should separate Maya Chen from Leo Santos instead of mixing us together.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:06:46.585553","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:04.744000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:15.480000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-2:1"},{"start":85.161,"end":95.935,"text":"Panic checkpoint, buenos días, Leo. Vexa convierte reuniones de Google Meet y Microsoft Teams en inteligencia de reuniones en tiempo real.","language":"es","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:06.590168","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:25.252000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:36.026000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-1:3"},{"start":85.966,"end":111.005,"text":"Да, осталось сходить в душ и копить почву.","language":"ru","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:26.596174","speaker":"Dmitriy Grankin","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:26.057000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:51.096000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-0:0"},{"start":102.946,"end":113.392,"text":"Prennent check point. Bonjour Maya. Les webhooks peuvent annoncer le statut de la réunion, les erreurs et la transcription finale.","language":"fr","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:26.596035","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:43.037000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:53.483000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-2:2"},{"start":118.387,"end":129.945,"text":"Nice. Back in English, a support team can use Vexa to capture customer calls, action items, objections, and promised follow-ups.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:07:46.601074","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:03:58.478000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:10.036000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-1:4"},{"start":153.989,"end":154.929,"text":"Português e Checkpoint.","language":"pt","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:16.617175","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:34.080000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:35.020000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-1:5"},{"start":154.929,"end":163.947,"text":"Rola Leo, infraestrutura Selfos teve ajuda a equipes a controlar lodos, armazenamento e retencal de gravacores.","language":"pt","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:16.617298","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:35.020000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:44.038000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-1:6"},{"start":163.947,"end":179.128,"text":"Rola Leo, infraestrutura Selfos, armazenamento e retencal de gravacores.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:36.644127","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:44.038000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:59.219000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-1:7"},{"start":164.768,"end":173.387,"text":"Good handoff. Maya. The self-hosted point matters because teams want reliable logs and predictable data boundaries.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:26.633979","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:44.859000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:04:53.478000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-2:3"},{"start":181.989,"end":192.029,"text":"For scoring, I am responsible for meeting intelligence, the API Gateway, self-hosted deployment and the final takeaway.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:46.653680","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:02.080000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:12.120000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-1:8"},{"start":193.547,"end":203.403,"text":"For scoring, I am responsible for Google Meet, Microsoft Teams, speaker labels, webhooks and recordings.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:08:56.665457","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:13.638000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:23.494000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-2:4"},{"start":206.369,"end":217.964,"text":"Leo, please confirm the operations report should include bot lifecycle, first transcript time, webhook delivery and stop status.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:09:06.674532","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:26.460000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:38.055000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-1:9"},{"start":222.026,"end":231.419,"text":"Confirmed, Maya. The report should also mention whether the dashboard updated in real time and whether playback or transcript artifacts are available.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:09:26.680497","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:42.117000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:51.510000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-2:5"},{"start":238.683,"end":249.96,"text":"My final takeaway is that Vexa turns live meeting audio into programmable meeting intelligence for real products.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:09:46.713658","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:05:58.774000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:10.051000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-1:10"},{"start":252.806,"end":261.433,"text":"My final takeaway is that this named two-speaker demo should prove the listener heard Maya and Leo clearly. End of podcast.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-24T10:09:56.725165","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:12.897000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:06:21.524000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-2:6"},{"start":261.433,"end":275.36,"text":"End of podcast.","language":"en","created_at":null,"speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-qoh-r4","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-24T10:09:19.295000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-24T10:09:33.222000Z","segment_id":"732d478b-52dd-469e-b708-c6d88ef3827b:speaker-2:7"}]}
